title: #92Noon! Vox In The Box: Bill Guerin, Dean Evason, Michael Russo, Marcus Foligno, Ryan Carter
description: Vox In The Box is back! Wild GM Bill Guerin joins to talk all things Wild, Head Coach Dean Evason joins to talk the current play and lines, Michael Russo joins to be...Russo, Wild Forward Marcus Foligno joins to talk about his season thus far, Former Wild and White Bear Lake Bear Ryan Carter brings his perspective about the Wild to the box.
